page.title: 05A TYPICAL DAY(CARL,AGE 11)
page.content: AT 7:30 I GET MY BREAKFAST.THEN I GO INTO THE BATHROOM AND GET A WASH.I GET DRESSED AND WAIT UNTIL 8:30,WHEN MY DAD GETS UP.AT 8:45 WE GO TO SCHOOL.AFTER REGISTER WE GO INTO ASSEMBLY,THIS BEING FOLLOWED WITH THE FIRST LESSON.AT 10:30 WE HAVE A 15 MINUTE BREAK BEFORE THE SECOND LESSON.DINNER IS FROM 12 UNTIL 1:15,WHEN THE THIRD LESSON BEGINS.BREAK AT 2:30 IS FOLLOWED BY THE FINAL LESSON,THIS LASTING UNTIL 3:45,WHEN WE GO HOME.I PUT ON THE TELEVISION UNTIL MY TEA IS READY.AFTER TEA I GO OUT TO PLAY UNTIL 9:00.BEDTIME IS AT 10:00
